This README file contains information on the contents of the meta-mylayer layer.

Please see the corresponding sections below for details.

Dependencies
============

 myrecipe:
  meta-oe -> nodejs


Table of Contents
=================

  I. Adding the meta-mylayer layer to your build
 II. Misc


I. Adding the meta-mylayer layer to your build
=================================================

Run 'bitbake-layers add-layer meta-mylayer'

II. Misc
========

NodeJS requires sse2 from CPU. QEMU doesn't always configure it automatically, thus
if building for QEMU, run QEMU with parameters "-cpu (fitting cpu arch here),+sse2"
